       NUT      TN
        |       | 
        |       |Initialize NUT (as a DHCPv6 Client)
        |       |
        | ----> |<B>Solicit</B>(1*)
        |       |
        |       |waiting for retransmitted message
        |       |
        | ----> |<B>Solicit</B>(2*)
